{"id":231702388,"title":"請益 濾掛式咖啡與咖啡粉","content":"想請教大家\n我不是那個專業的咖啡愛好者\n主要平常都用濾掛式咖啡來泡 \n加鮮奶來喝😂\n最近覺得 \n每天開一包濾掛式來喝有點不太夠\n濾掛式又不適合回沖 味道會不對\n所以想說雖然一天兩包濾掛式有點奢侈\n還是要給他買下去😓\n\n結果今天去超市剛好看到這種罐裝咖啡粉\nhttps://i.imgur.com/nQRQDZq.jpg\n不知道大家覺得他跟濾掛式泡出來\n感覺有沒有差不多？\n還有就是這種是直接用水沖開就可以嗎\n還是要用濾紙沖（濾紙我也有 不怕）\n\n我不是那種專業的😭😭\n舌頭也沒有厲害到能嚐出差別\n只要跟濾掛式沖出的差不多就行😂\n請大家不吝賜教","excerpt":"想請教大家，我不是那個專業的咖啡愛好者，主要平常都用濾掛式咖啡來泡，加鮮奶來喝，最近覺得，每天開一包濾掛式來喝有點不太夠，濾掛式又不適合回沖 味道會不對，所以想說雖然一天兩包濾掛式有點奢侈，還是要給他","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"6120536f-6a70-49bb-8891-ec0ba2f4b396","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-07-19T07:22:49.185Z","updatedAt":"2019-07-19T07:22:49.185Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":8,"tags":[],"topics":[],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"咖啡","forumAlias":"coffee","school":"淡江大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":8}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/nQRQDZq.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"82e41eb8-72cb-4ab7-a716-db0b0ceee25f","url":"https://i.imgur.com/nQRQDZq.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/nQRQDZq.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/nQRQDZq.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-07-19T07:22:49.185Z","updatedAt":"2019-07-19T07:22:49.185Z"},{"id":"82e41eb8-72cb-4ab7-a716-db0b0ceee25f","url":"https://i.imgur.com/nQRQDZq.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/nQRQDZq.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/nQRQDZq.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-07-19T07:22:49.185Z","updatedAt":"2019-07-19T07:22:49.185Z"}],"postAvatar":""}